Katharine Lee McEwan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katharine_Lee_McEwan 0 Katharine Lee McEwan is an English actress, screenwriter, and film producer. She gained recognition in 2015 with the award-winning independent feature film Solitary, which she wrote and produced in addition to playing the lead role.
